title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table within a grid cell
description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table located inside a grid cell.
OB: Upon exporting data from a table within a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: Exporting data from a table within a grid cell should not result in any exceptions.
SR:
1. Create a grid.
2. Insert a table into one grid cell.
3. Insert another table into another grid cell.
4. Attempt to export data from either table within the grid cells.
